<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTA82">
<l>terintuṇarvoṉ ṟiṉmaiyā ṟīviṉaiyēṉ vāḷā</l>
<l>viruntoḻintēṉ kīḻnāḷka ḷellāṅ karanturuvi</l>
<l>lammāṉai yaññāṉṟu piṉṭoṭarnta vāḻiyaṅkai</l>
<l>yammāṉai yēttā tayarntu.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>All days are base of me staying behind silently, me with evil deeds,</l>
<l>in the absence of any perception with understanding – [days] occupied</l>
<l>without praising the father with the discus in [his] palm who that day</l>
<l>followed after that deer, having hidden in [another] form.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
